               ~%~10d subtype judgements~
               ~%~10d constant judgements~
               ~%~10d conversions~
               ~%~10d TCCs~
               ~%~10d axioms~
               ~%~10d postulates~
               ~%~10d formulas"
      utdecls tdecls consts defs recs inds coinds subjdgs jdgs convs
